00:25:14,640 --> 00:25:16,700
 taj preliminarni postupak.

766
00:25:16,700 --> 00:25:18,780
 Što se tiče

767
00:25:18,780 --> 00:25:19,520
 tog samog

768
00:25:19,520 --> 00:25:21,540
 preliminarnog postupka,

769
00:25:21,540 --> 00:25:22,800
 ne znam ko je

770
00:25:22,800 --> 00:25:23,600
 saslušan

771
00:25:23,600 --> 00:25:24,020
 osim

772
00:25:24,020 --> 00:25:25,520
 navodne žrtve,

773
00:25:26,460 --> 00:25:28,900
 ali niko nije došao na,

774
00:25:28,900 --> 00:25:31,380
 niko nije saslušan od osoba

775
00:25:31,380 --> 00:25:32,040
 koje su,

776
00:25:32,040 --> 00:25:33,080
 znači,

777
00:25:33,080 --> 00:25:35,660
 živjele skoro godinu danas

778
00:25:35,660 --> 00:25:36,780
 sa navodnom žrtvom.

779
00:25:36,780 --> 00:25:37,360
 Znači,

780
00:25:37,360 --> 00:25:39,820
 niko nije saslušan od njih,

781
00:25:39,820 --> 00:25:42,440
 nije saslušan don Josip,

782
00:25:42,440 --> 00:25:43,580
 nije saslušana

783
00:25:43,580 --> 00:25:45,640
 majka Josefina,

784
00:25:45,640 --> 00:25:48,660
 ne vjerim da je saslušan

785
00:25:48,660 --> 00:25:50,280
 ni njeni suprug,

786
00:25:50,280 --> 00:25:50,860
 znači,

787
00:25:50,860 --> 00:25:51,440
 to se...

788
00:25:51,440 --> 00:25:53,220
 Zato nije obveza u pravilima

789
00:25:53,220 --> 00:25:55,000
 da se sasluša jedna i druga strana,

790
00:25:55,000 --> 00:25:55,300
 mislim,

791
00:25:55,300 --> 00:25:57,120
 postoje dosta razrađena ta pravila,

792
00:25:57,120 --> 00:25:58,960
 mi smo čak i pisali o tome da se...

793
00:25:58,960 --> 00:25:59,580
 Evo, uglavnom,

794
00:25:59,580 --> 00:26:00,520
 mi vam govorimo,

795
00:26:00,520 --> 00:26:02,260
 ja ne znam kojim su se,

796
00:26:02,260 --> 00:26:05,480
 zašto su se vodili tim načinom,

797
00:26:05,480 --> 00:26:06,060
 ali uglavnom,

798
00:26:06,060 --> 00:26:07,260
 s naše strane,

799
00:26:07,260 --> 00:26:08,500
 niko nije kontaktiran,

800
00:26:08,500 --> 00:26:09,700
 s druge strane,

801
00:26:09,700 --> 00:26:10,600
 kažem vam,

802
00:26:10,600 --> 00:26:11,280
 niti su se,

803
00:26:11,280 --> 00:26:13,300
 niti je iko pokušao

804
00:26:13,300 --> 00:26:14,780
 rekonstruirati

805
00:26:14,780 --> 00:26:15,800
 gdje se to dogodilo,

806
00:26:15,800 --> 00:26:16,300
 mjesto,

807
00:26:16,300 --> 00:26:17,560
 ja ne znam,

808
00:26:17,560 --> 00:26:21,660
 da li se vodi o tome računa,

809
00:26:21,660 --> 00:26:23,320
 zato što niko nije došao na to mjesto

810
00:26:23,320 --> 00:26:24,140
 da to pogleda,

811
00:26:24,140 --> 00:26:25,140
 gdje se to dogodilo.

812
00:26:25,740 --> 00:26:26,520
 To vam mogu tvrditi,

813
00:26:26,520 --> 00:26:29,480
 zato što znao bi da je neko došao

814
00:26:29,480 --> 00:26:30,640
 posjetiti sestre,

815
00:26:30,640 --> 00:26:31,240
 pa da vidi,

816
00:26:31,240 --> 00:26:33,560
 aha, tu se to eventualno događalo.

817
00:26:33,560 --> 00:26:35,320
 Niko nije napravio to

818
00:26:35,320 --> 00:26:36,520
 da izađe na mjesto,

819
00:26:36,520 --> 00:26:37,180
 da vidi,

820
00:26:37,180 --> 00:26:38,460
 evo, tu je to bilo.

821
00:26:38,460 --> 00:26:40,600
 Tako da...

822
00:26:40,600 --> 00:26:41,060
 Jasno mi je.

823
00:26:41,060 --> 00:26:42,660
 Kako ste zapravo vi doznali to

824
00:26:42,660 --> 00:26:43,560
 u zajednici?

825
00:26:43,560 --> 00:26:45,400
 Jeste doznali službenim kanalima

826
00:26:45,400 --> 00:26:46,760
 ili službenim kanalima?

827
00:26:46,760 --> 00:26:47,320
 Znači ovako,

828
00:26:47,320 --> 00:26:50,340
 ja sam do 23. lipnja

829
00:26:50,340 --> 00:26:52,260
 uručeno nam...

830
00:26:52,260 --> 00:26:53,040
 25. ove godine, da.

831
00:26:53,040 --> 00:26:54,200
 Da, da, ove godine

832
00:26:54,200 --> 00:26:56,140
 su nam u...

833
00:26:56,140 --> 00:26:58,380
 zapravo doniosip je tada

834
00:26:58,380 --> 00:27:00,420
 rečeno mi da je

835
00:27:00,420 --> 00:27:03,000
 maknut sa uprave zajednice,

836
00:27:03,000 --> 00:27:04,020
 ja je preuzimam.

837
00:27:04,980 --> 00:27:05,500
 Zbog toga?

838
00:27:05,500 --> 00:27:06,420
 Zbog toga.

839
00:27:06,420 --> 00:27:07,880
 A jeste li to tada znali

840
00:27:07,880 --> 00:27:08,300
 da se to...

841
00:27:08,300 --> 00:27:09,020
 Makak, ništa.

842
00:27:09,020 --> 00:27:09,780
 Znači vi ste

843
00:27:09,780 --> 00:27:11,820
 instalirani, doniosip je nakon

844
00:27:11,820 --> 00:27:12,780
 da niste znali...

845
00:27:12,780 --> 00:27:14,680
 Nismo znali do toga časa,

846
00:27:14,680 --> 00:27:15,900
 nismo znali zbog čega.

847
00:27:15,900 --> 00:27:18,000
 Tek tada je prvi put

848
00:27:18,000 --> 00:27:20,060
 rečeno o čemu se radi.

849
00:27:20,060 --> 00:27:22,120
 Mi nismo ne slutili.

850
00:27:22,120 --> 00:27:24,240
 Ono što sam ja odmah pito

851
00:27:24,240 --> 00:27:25,080
 istoga časa,

852
00:27:25,080 --> 00:27:28,120
 pito sam da li je to

853
00:27:28,120 --> 00:27:30,120
 prijavljeno civilnim vlastima.

854
00:27:30,120 --> 00:27:30,980
 Znači istoga časa

855
00:27:30,980 --> 00:27:32,360
 kad mi je uručen taj papir

856
00:27:32,360 --> 00:27:32,860
 sam pito,

857
00:27:32,860 --> 00:27:33,840
 rečeno mi je da je

858
00:27:33,840 --> 00:27:34,900
 i to je to.

859
00:27:34,980 --> 00:27:39,480
 i onda moj zadatak je bio

860
00:27:39,480 --> 00:27:40,940
 odmah kroz kratko vrijeme,

861
00:27:40,940 --> 00:27:42,060
 ja sam odmah to učinio

862
00:27:42,060 --> 00:27:43,080
 kroz dva, tri dana

863
00:27:43,080 --> 00:27:44,260
 u nadom domu,

864
00:27:44,260 --> 00:27:46,540
 obavijestio cijelu zajednicu.

865
00:27:46,540 --> 00:27:47,500
 Mi smo se skupili

866
00:27:47,500 --> 00:27:48,820
 i svima sam priopćio

867
00:27:48,820 --> 00:27:50,640
 što se...

868
00:27:50,640 --> 00:27:52,200
 Znači svima se pročitao

869
00:27:52,200 --> 00:27:53,160
 cijeli dopis.

870
00:27:53,160 --> 00:27:54,440
 Cijeli dopis i tako.

871
00:27:54,440 --> 00:27:58,200
 Sa svim optužbama i tako dalje.

872
00:27:58,200 --> 00:27:59,480
 E sad to što govorite

873
00:27:59,480 --> 00:28:01,260
 povezano je s vašim odlaskom

874
00:28:01,260 --> 00:28:02,300
 iz svjetskih sela.

875
00:28:02,300 --> 00:28:03,400
 Sad je to vrlo važno.

876
00:28:03,400 --> 00:28:05,160
 Dakle, mnogi su se pitali

877
00:28:05,160 --> 00:28:05,980
 što su različita

878
00:28:05,980 --> 00:28:07,460
 nagađenja kuluarske priče.

879
00:28:07,460 --> 00:28:07,700
 Naime,

880
00:28:07,700 --> 00:28:09,380
 ako netko ne zna,

881
00:28:09,380 --> 00:28:11,080
 zajednica Omnija Deo

882
00:28:11,080 --> 00:28:11,640
 je bila

883
00:28:11,640 --> 00:28:13,900
 u župi Svjetska sela,

884
00:28:13,900 --> 00:28:14,580
 odnosno svetištu

885
00:28:14,580 --> 00:28:16,100
 svetog Antuna Padovanskoga.

886
00:28:16,100 --> 00:28:17,960
 Vi ste ondje došli

887
00:28:17,960 --> 00:28:19,280
 na zahtjev,

888
00:28:19,280 --> 00:28:20,380
 odnosno na preporuku

889
00:28:20,380 --> 00:28:21,400
 i intervenciju

890
00:28:21,400 --> 00:28:22,560
 Zagrebačkog nadbiskupa.

891
00:28:23,400 --> 00:28:24,140
 koliko ja znam,

892
00:28:24,140 --> 00:28:25,460
 evo mogu to čak i javno reći,

893
00:28:25,460 --> 00:28:27,160
 napisao sam da vas je na neki način

894
00:28:27,160 --> 00:28:29,400
 on malo možda je tu i protežirao,

895
00:28:29,400 --> 00:28:30,300
 ajmo to tako reći,

896
00:28:30,300 --> 00:28:31,980
 da ste došli kao nekakva njegova

897
00:28:31,980 --> 00:28:34,480
 pod navodnicima elita

898
00:28:34,480 --> 00:28:35,860
 i tu se na vas malo gledalo,

899
00:28:35,860 --> 00:28:37,260
 ja znam od nekih svećenika,

900
00:28:37,260 --> 00:28:39,020
 sa ljubomorom i možda zavišću,

901
00:28:39,020 --> 00:28:40,000
 onako jednom tipičnom

902
00:28:40,000 --> 00:28:41,900
 za svećenički posao.

903
00:28:42,900 --> 00:28:44,080
 i koliko se zna,

904
00:28:44,080 --> 00:28:46,300
 radili ste tamo jako dobro,

905
00:28:46,300 --> 00:28:47,560
 crkva je bila stalno puna,

906
00:28:47,560 --> 00:28:48,900
 ja znam ljude koji živeo ondje,

907
00:28:48,900 --> 00:28:50,500
 kažu ne možeš doći na red za ispovjed,

908
00:28:50,500 --> 00:28:51,500
 ispovjed,

909
00:28:51,500 --> 00:28:54,080
 kilometarski su redove i tako dalje

910
00:28:54,080 --> 00:28:56,120
 i u tom se trenutku dogodio

911
00:28:56,120 --> 00:28:57,420
 taj lom o kojem vi govorite,

912
00:28:57,420 --> 00:28:59,740
 evo mi do sada ne znamo što se dogodilo,

913
00:28:59,740 --> 00:29:01,900
 vi nestajete iz sestvjetskih sela

914
00:29:01,900 --> 00:29:02,700
 i svi se pitaju

915
00:29:02,700 --> 00:29:04,040
 zašto je Omnija deo,

916
00:29:04,040 --> 00:29:05,060
 ja sam čak i nadbiskupa

917
00:29:05,060 --> 00:29:06,240
 u intervju za večerni list

918
00:29:06,240 --> 00:29:06,680
 pitao,

919
00:29:06,680 --> 00:29:09,600
 kada je to objavljeno u premištajima,

920
00:29:10,020 --> 00:29:11,740
 što se dogodilo sa zajednicom Omnija deo,

921
00:29:11,740 --> 00:29:13,800
 on je tada rekao da je jedan vaš kapelan

922
00:29:13,800 --> 00:29:16,080
 ostao ondje u sestvjetskih srema,

923
00:29:16,080 --> 00:29:17,760
 evo pa vas molim da nam ispričate

924
00:29:17,760 --> 00:29:19,000
 i taj dio priče.

925
00:29:19,000 --> 00:29:20,260
 Tada je,

926
00:29:20,260 --> 00:29:23,000
 ja sam postao povjerenik,

927
00:29:23,000 --> 00:29:27,120
 ja sam svakako morao se posvetiti zajednici,

928
00:29:27,120 --> 00:29:30,400
 da li je zajednica morala

929
00:29:30,400 --> 00:29:32,180
 ili nije trebala odlaziti sa sela,

930
00:29:32,180 --> 00:29:33,920
 to ja ne znam,

931
00:29:33,920 --> 00:29:35,380
 ne ulazim u odluke,

932
00:29:35,380 --> 00:29:36,240
 ja ih poštujem

933
00:29:36,240 --> 00:29:37,180
 i uvijek,

934
00:29:37,180 --> 00:29:39,180
 znači na svakome mjestu poštujem

935
00:29:39,180 --> 00:29:41,940
 svaku odluku crkvene vlasti,

936
00:29:41,940 --> 00:29:42,480
 biskupa,

937
00:29:42,480 --> 00:29:43,280
 nadbiskupa,

938
00:29:43,280 --> 00:29:44,440
 svetog oca,

939
00:29:44,440 --> 00:29:46,340
 to je jedna od karizmi naše zajednice.

940
00:29:46,340 --> 00:29:47,960
 Apsolutna poslušnost,

941
00:29:47,960 --> 00:29:50,220
 odnosno nešto što je u temelju karizme,

942
00:29:50,220 --> 00:29:50,760
 bez čega,

943
00:29:50,760 --> 00:29:52,840
 ja sam kad sam postao svećenik,

944
00:29:52,840 --> 00:29:53,420
 to odabrao.

945
00:29:53,420 --> 00:29:56,840
 Bez rezervnu poslušnost crkvi,

946
00:29:56,840 --> 00:29:58,900
 svetom ocu i biskupu,

947
00:29:58,900 --> 00:30:00,100
 ordinariju.

948
00:30:00,420 --> 00:30:01,360
 u tome trenutku,

949
00:30:01,360 --> 00:30:03,240
 ja sam boravio na području

950
00:30:03,240 --> 00:30:04,380
 Zagrebaške nadbiskupije,

951
00:30:04,380 --> 00:30:05,420
 moj ordinariji je

952
00:30:05,420 --> 00:30:06,880
 nadbiskupi,

953
00:30:06,880 --> 00:30:09,000
 tu nema nikakvog pogovora.

954
00:30:09,000 --> 00:30:14,780
 Problem je što je to izazvalo,

955
00:30:14,780 --> 00:30:15,640
 ovo što ste vi rekli,

956
00:30:15,640 --> 00:30:17,560
 veliku konfuziju

957
00:30:17,560 --> 00:30:20,200
 međunarodom.

958
00:30:20,200 --> 00:30:20,560
 Zašto?

959
00:30:20,560 --> 00:30:22,100
 Zato što mi smo taman došli,

960
00:30:22,100 --> 00:30:25,700
 dvije godine započeli puno,

961
00:30:25,700 --> 00:30:27,840
 ovo što ste i sami rekli,

962
00:30:27,840 --> 00:30:29,260
 bilo je puno lijepih stvari.

963
00:30:29,260 --> 00:30:30,340
 Radili smo srcem,

964
00:30:30,340 --> 00:30:32,240
 ko što rade sva naša braća

965
00:30:32,240 --> 00:30:33,600
 po svim župama,

966
00:30:33,600 --> 00:30:34,860
 trude se, muče se,

967
00:30:34,860 --> 00:30:37,220
 rade srcem,

968
00:30:37,220 --> 00:30:38,400
 nemaju radno vrijeme.

969
00:30:38,400 --> 00:30:41,760
 I slušaju ljude,

970
00:30:41,760 --> 00:30:42,360
 ispovijedaju,

971
00:30:42,360 --> 00:30:43,660
 tako smo i mi ovdje radili.

972
00:30:43,660 --> 00:30:48,960
 I na jedan put dolazi to

973
00:30:48,960 --> 00:30:51,700
 da moramo se maknu,

974
00:30:51,700 --> 00:30:53,160
 što smo mi srcem prihvatili.

975
00:30:53,160 --> 00:30:55,020
 Normalno da je to izazvalo konfuziju.

976
00:30:55,020 --> 00:30:57,300
 Dio naroda je čak počeo

977
00:30:57,300 --> 00:30:58,220
 pisati peticiju,

978
00:30:58,220 --> 00:30:59,560
 da nas ostavi i tako dalje,

979
00:30:59,560 --> 00:31:01,380
 koja nikad nije krenula od nas

980
00:31:01,380 --> 00:31:02,340
 taman posla,

981
00:31:02,340 --> 00:31:04,300
 da bi pokretao tako.

982
00:31:04,300 --> 00:31:05,340
 Cijeli život sam dao

983
00:31:05,340 --> 00:31:06,300
 za Boga i za crkvu,

984
00:31:06,300 --> 00:31:07,820
 pa ću sad krenuti,

985
00:31:07,820 --> 00:31:11,480
 sad sam zbog toga ću

986
00:31:11,480 --> 00:31:15,900
 pokretati neke peticije.

987
00:31:15,900 --> 00:31:18,520
 To je izazvalo veliko komešanje u narodu.

988
00:31:18,960 --> 00:31:19,500
 Razumijete?

989
00:31:19,500 --> 00:31:21,640
 I onda su se pojavile

990
00:31:21,640 --> 00:31:22,780
 različite spekulacije,

991
00:31:22,780 --> 00:31:24,100
 pa ne miče se tako lako

992
00:31:24,100 --> 00:31:26,420
 ljude zbog ničega.

993
00:31:26,420 --> 00:31:29,700
 I onda je u jednom trenutku

994
00:31:29,700 --> 00:31:32,040
 da bi spriječio širenje

995
00:31:32,040 --> 00:31:34,700
 takvih sablazni među ljudima.

996
00:31:34,700 --> 00:31:37,340
 Tomo...

997
00:31:37,340 --> 00:31:39,920
 Da, pomislim točno je reći,

998
00:31:39,920 --> 00:31:41,620
 rećemo iskreno,

999
00:31:41,620 --> 00:31:43,980
 znači, kao i sve što govorimo.

1000
00:31:43,980 --> 00:31:47,540
 Stvari u tome,

1001
00:31:47,540 --> 00:31:48,840
 znači, kad se dogodila,

1002
00:31:48,840 --> 00:31:51,360
 recimo, ta promjena,

1003
00:31:51,360 --> 00:31:52,720
 mi, ja i Giuliano,

1004
00:31:52,720 --> 00:31:54,560
 smo to, ja sam prihvatio,

1005
00:31:54,560 --> 00:31:56,660
 mislim, došao sam tu,

1006
00:31:57,820 --> 00:31:59,040
 stavljen sam tu,

1007
00:31:59,040 --> 00:32:00,640
 primio sam tu,

1008
00:32:00,640 --> 00:32:01,620
 uzelo,

1009
00:32:01,620 --> 00:32:02,660
 odnosno,

1010
00:32:02,660 --> 00:32:04,540
 razviješen sam,

1011
00:32:04,540 --> 00:32:07,260
 men to nije bio problem.

1012
00:32:07,260 --> 00:32:08,960
 Ono što je sigurno

1013
00:32:08,960 --> 00:32:09,820
 najveći problem

1014
00:32:09,820 --> 00:32:11,900
 bio taj što

1015
00:32:11,900 --> 00:32:15,600
 dio ljudi je prije nas znao

1016
00:32:15,600 --> 00:32:17,820
 da će nas maknuti.

1017
00:32:18,980 --> 00:32:19,720
 dio ljudi,

1018
00:32:19,720 --> 00:32:21,240
 svećenika ili dio

1019
00:32:21,240 --> 00:32:22,520
 lajka,

1020
00:32:22,520 --> 00:32:22,900
 kazada.

1021
00:32:22,900 --> 00:32:24,040
 I svećenika i lajka.

1022
00:32:24,040 --> 00:32:24,560
 I svećenika i lajka.

1023
00:32:24,560 --> 00:32:25,200
 I jedno i druga.

1024
00:32:25,200 --> 00:32:25,920
 I jedno i druga, da.

1025
00:32:25,920 --> 00:32:28,860
 I krenula je ta priča

1026
00:32:28,860 --> 00:32:29,940
 ko što inače,

1027
00:32:29,940 --> 00:32:30,620
 ono,

1028
00:32:30,620 --> 00:32:32,100
 nas dosta znaju

1029
00:32:32,100 --> 00:32:35,740
 raznim tvrdnjama

1030
00:32:35,740 --> 00:32:36,480
 o Basipat,

1031
00:32:36,480 --> 00:32:37,600
 koje su na istine,

1032
00:32:37,600 --> 00:32:39,620
 da smo ja i Giuliano

1033
00:32:39,620 --> 00:32:42,040
 optuženi zbog pedofilije,

1034
00:32:42,040 --> 00:32:43,200
 da smo pokrali

1035
00:32:43,200 --> 00:32:45,320
 700, 800 tišća eura

1036
00:32:45,320 --> 00:32:46,320
 i tako.

1037
00:32:46,320 --> 00:32:48,460
 Mi smo čekali tu možda

1038
00:32:48,460 --> 00:32:49,720
 sad ne znam,

1039
00:32:49,720 --> 00:32:51,680
 tjedan ili dva koliko je bilo,

1040
00:32:51,680 --> 00:32:53,700
 a razgovarali smo.

1041
00:32:53,700 --> 00:32:55,220
 To se širilo,

1042
00:32:55,220 --> 00:32:56,780
 jako je ljude pogađalo.

1043
00:32:56,780 --> 00:32:59,280
 Vidjeli smo da to ne jenjava

1044
00:32:59,280 --> 00:33:02,900
 i onda smo odlučili,

1045
00:33:02,900 --> 00:33:04,460
 budući da je

1046
00:33:04,460 --> 00:33:06,840
 sama situacija takav,

1047
00:33:06,840 --> 00:33:08,260
 ja imam nečake

1048
00:33:08,260 --> 00:33:09,940
 koji idu u školu

1049
00:33:09,940 --> 00:33:11,280
 tu blizu i tako,

1050
00:33:11,280 --> 00:33:13,300
 da djecačevi,

1051
00:33:13,300 --> 00:33:14,020
 da je uvijek,

1052
00:33:14,020 --> 00:33:15,480
 razumijete me,

1053
00:33:15,480 --> 00:33:18,040
 optužen zbog

1054
00:33:18,040 --> 00:33:18,660
 pedofilije,

1055
00:33:18,660 --> 00:33:20,000
 da sam pokrao novce,

1056
00:33:20,000 --> 00:33:22,120
 a s druge strane,

1057
00:33:22,120 --> 00:33:23,760
 sam sam jako puno

1058
00:33:23,760 --> 00:33:25,780
 ispovjedao djecu,

1059
00:33:25,780 --> 00:33:26,940
 radio s djecom

1060
00:33:26,940 --> 00:33:29,440
 i mladi sa mladima.

1061
00:33:29,440 --> 00:33:31,360
 Jednostavno sam,

1062
00:33:31,360 --> 00:33:33,760
 napravili smo to jedno

1063
00:33:33,760 --> 00:33:34,520
 priopćenje,

1064
00:33:34,520 --> 00:33:36,380
 koje sam ja pročitao

1065
00:33:36,380 --> 00:33:37,280
 srcem,

1066
00:33:39,020 --> 00:33:39,580
 iskreno,

1067
00:33:39,580 --> 00:33:40,400
 otvoreno,

1068
00:33:40,400 --> 00:33:42,360
 i onda sam čuo

1069
00:33:42,360 --> 00:33:44,360
 da su mnogi ga dijelili,

1070
00:33:44,360 --> 00:33:46,080
 neko je to snimio.

1071
00:33:46,080 --> 00:33:46,640
 Evo, priznajem,

1072
00:33:46,640 --> 00:33:47,960
 ja sam ga dobio na Whatsapp

1073
00:33:47,960 --> 00:33:48,920
 i ja sam ga preslušao.

1074
00:33:48,920 --> 00:33:50,220
 Bilo je onako dosta emotivno

1075
00:33:50,220 --> 00:33:51,660
 nabirano za sve naše gledateljike,

1076
00:33:51,660 --> 00:33:52,000
 ne znam,

1077
00:33:52,000 --> 00:33:54,480
 bilo je to dosta emocija.

1078
00:33:54,660 --> 00:33:56,260
 Da, neko je to snimio,

1079
00:33:56,260 --> 00:33:57,700
 ovaj...

1080
00:33:57,700 --> 00:33:58,940
 I neovlašteno posto.

1081
00:33:58,940 --> 00:33:59,480
 I neovlašteno posto.

1082
00:33:59,480 --> 00:33:59,820
 Jasno, jasno.

1083
00:33:59,820 --> 00:34:02,300
 Proslijedio to je isključivo,

1084
00:34:02,300 --> 00:34:03,740
 bilo znači namjenjeno

1085
00:34:03,740 --> 00:34:06,040
 samo za naše župljane,

1086
00:34:06,040 --> 00:34:07,200
 tamo koji dolaze,

1087
00:34:07,200 --> 00:34:10,040
 koji su bili pogođeni time

1088
00:34:10,040 --> 00:34:10,620
 i tako,

1089
00:34:10,620 --> 00:34:12,400
 jer to je masa djece,

1090
00:34:12,400 --> 00:34:16,160
 mladih obitelji,

1091
00:34:16,160 --> 00:34:17,280
 mladih obitelji,

1092
00:34:17,280 --> 00:34:17,960
 mladi ljudi,

1093
00:34:17,960 --> 00:34:19,860
 jer samo da imate za primjer

1094
00:34:19,860 --> 00:34:20,340
 jedan,

1095
00:34:20,340 --> 00:34:22,960
 od kad smo mi došli na Sesecka,

1096
00:34:23,180 --> 00:34:25,440
 na župu Svetog Antona Padovanskog,

1097
00:34:25,440 --> 00:34:27,040
 mi smo znali dnevno

1098
00:34:27,040 --> 00:34:29,060
 ispovjedati po 4-5 sati.

1099
00:34:29,060 --> 00:34:30,280
 Svaki dan?

1100
00:34:30,280 --> 00:34:31,060
 Svaki dan.

1101
00:34:31,060 --> 00:34:33,240
 Nedeljom po 10 sati.

1102
00:34:33,240 --> 00:34:34,600
 Kad govorite 4-5 sati,

1103
00:34:34,600 --> 00:34:35,220
 to je ukupno

1104
00:34:35,220 --> 00:34:36,480
 ili svaki svećenik po 4?

1105
00:34:36,480 --> 00:34:37,740
 Koliko vas je znali ispovjediti?

1106
00:34:37,740 --> 00:34:38,920
 Svaki posebno.

1107
00:34:38,920 --> 00:34:40,500
 Znači, ja i Đuljano,

1108
00:34:40,500 --> 00:34:41,560
 kad bi ispovjedali,

1109
00:34:41,560 --> 00:34:42,100
 recimo,

1110
00:34:42,100 --> 00:34:44,500
 kad bi krenuli u 5,

1111
00:34:44,500 --> 00:34:45,380
 znači,

1112
00:34:45,380 --> 00:34:47,060
 popodne završili bi,

1113
00:34:47,060 --> 00:34:47,520
 recimo,

1114
00:34:47,520 --> 00:34:49,020
 do 10-11.

1115
00:34:49,020 --> 00:34:50,040
 Ja sam znao nekad

1116
00:34:50,040 --> 00:34:51,660
 završiti u 1 ujutro.

1117
00:34:52,900 --> 00:34:54,160
 jer bude ljudi do...

1118
00:34:54,160 --> 00:34:56,320
 Dolazili su iz drugih dijelova grada,

1119
00:34:56,320 --> 00:34:57,940
 ne samo iz drugih gradova čak.

1120
00:34:57,940 --> 00:35:00,340
 Da, pa znate što je kada...

1121
00:35:00,340 --> 00:35:01,440
 Evo sad sam vidio

1122
00:35:01,440 --> 00:35:03,480
 i u Bazilice Svetoga Petra,

1123
00:35:03,480 --> 00:35:05,560
 što je napravljena

1124
00:35:05,560 --> 00:35:07,160
 jedna jako lijepa gesta.

1125
00:35:08,040 --> 00:35:09,180
 imaju ispovjeda once,

1126
00:35:09,180 --> 00:35:10,360
 ljudi za ispovjed,

1127
00:35:10,360 --> 00:35:14,660
 a imaju baš mjesta logi diaskolto,

1128
00:35:14,660 --> 00:35:16,300
 mjesta za slušanje.

1129
00:35:16,300 --> 00:35:18,600
 Jer vidite danas

1130
00:35:18,600 --> 00:35:21,500
 i vi susrećete se s time kao čovjek

1131
00:35:21,500 --> 00:35:22,720
 u naše vrijeme,

1132
00:35:22,720 --> 00:35:23,300
 mehanizacije,

1133
00:35:23,300 --> 00:35:25,380
 tehnike i svega.

1134
00:35:25,380 --> 00:35:29,340
 Često se zanemari to da se čuje drugoga,

1135
00:35:29,340 --> 00:35:31,360
 da se osjeti njegovo bilo

1136
00:35:31,360 --> 00:35:33,180
 i nažalost svi smo u opasnosti,

1137
00:35:33,180 --> 00:35:36,120
 a osobno da to zanemarimo.

1138
00:35:36,120 --> 00:35:39,220
 A u našoj karizmi,

1139
00:35:39,220 --> 00:35:41,020
 ovo što je rekao Don Julijano,

1140
00:35:41,020 --> 00:35:43,940
 je upravo taj sakrament ispovjedi

1141
00:35:43,940 --> 00:35:45,700
 koje učiteljstvo crkve

1142
00:35:45,700 --> 00:35:46,780
 na čelu s papama

1143
00:35:46,780 --> 00:35:49,240
 jako zagovara, promiče

1144
00:35:49,240 --> 00:35:51,120
 i podupire.

1145
00:35:51,120 --> 00:35:53,300
 Posebno evo naš dragi svetac

1146
00:35:53,300 --> 00:35:54,260
 Ivan Pavao II.

1147
00:35:54,260 --> 00:35:56,340
 koji je rekao da je to

1148
00:35:56,340 --> 00:35:59,920
 temeljni i najbitniji

1149
00:35:59,920 --> 00:36:01,320
 dio pastirske službe

1150
00:36:01,320 --> 00:36:03,640
 svećenika sveta ispovjedi,

1151
00:36:03,640 --> 00:36:05,300
 sakrament svete ispovjedi

1152
00:36:05,300 --> 00:36:07,340
 i ta jedna otvorenost

1153
00:36:07,340 --> 00:36:09,420
 prije svega da se drugog prihvati

1154
00:36:09,420 --> 00:36:10,460
 kroz slušanje.

1155
00:36:10,460 --> 00:36:13,280
 I mi smo tu se stvarno

1156
00:36:13,280 --> 00:36:14,740
 trudili.

1157
00:36:14,740 --> 00:36:17,480
 Tu prvu godinu smo jako puno

1158
00:36:17,480 --> 00:36:19,440
 uložili u to

1159
00:36:19,440 --> 00:36:21,740
 bez radnog vremena,

1160
00:36:21,740 --> 00:36:22,740
 bez hrane,

1161
00:36:22,740 --> 00:36:23,860
 bez pića,

1162
00:36:23,860 --> 00:36:25,620
 bez tanki.

1163
00:36:25,620 --> 00:36:27,920
 Jednostavno smo primali ljude

1164
00:36:27,920 --> 00:36:30,320
 što na duhovne razgovore,

1165
00:36:30,460 --> 00:36:31,440
 što na molitve,

1166
00:36:31,440 --> 00:36:34,260
 što na ispovjedi

1167
00:36:34,260 --> 00:36:36,440
 i naravno to je donijelo,

1168
00:36:36,440 --> 00:36:38,420
 stvorilo jedan efekt.

1169
00:36:38,420 --> 00:36:40,640
 Što je meni bilo

1170
00:36:40,640 --> 00:36:42,280
 nevjerojatna nagrada

1171
00:36:42,280 --> 00:36:43,600
 u mome svećeništu,

1172
00:36:43,600 --> 00:36:46,060
 kad dođe dijete četvrti razred

1173
00:36:46,060 --> 00:36:46,620
 i kaže,

1174
00:36:46,620 --> 00:36:47,340
 ono,

1175
00:36:47,340 --> 00:36:48,100
 velečasne,

1176
00:36:48,100 --> 00:36:49,560
 predivno se osjećam,

1177
00:36:49,560 --> 00:36:50,960
 bolji sam,

1178
00:36:50,960 --> 00:36:52,400
 bolja sam prema mami,

1179
00:36:52,400 --> 00:36:53,320
 prema tati,

1180
00:36:53,320 --> 00:36:54,260
 sve je bolje.

1181
00:36:55,040 --> 00:36:55,260
 onda,

1182
00:36:55,260 --> 00:36:57,240
 ili kad vam neki roditelj kaže,

1183
00:36:57,240 --> 00:36:57,940
 ono,

1184
00:36:57,940 --> 00:37:00,180
 rekla mi je čerka,

1185
00:37:00,180 --> 00:37:02,620
 nisam se dugo ispovjedio,

1186
00:37:02,620 --> 00:37:03,020
 evo,

1187
00:37:03,020 --> 00:37:04,420
 obidošao i onda,

1188
00:37:04,420 --> 00:37:05,880
 vidite jednostavno,

1189
00:37:05,880 --> 00:37:09,320
 mi često govorimo riječima,

1190
00:37:09,320 --> 00:37:11,400
 svjedočimo raznim stvarima,

1191
00:37:11,760 --> 00:37:13,420
 ali nema jačeg svjedočanstva,

1192
00:37:13,420 --> 00:37:15,000
 svjedočanstva srca.

1193
00:37:15,000 --> 00:37:16,360
 Sad zamislite,

1194
00:37:16,360 --> 00:37:18,260
 jednog roditelja,

1195
00:37:18,260 --> 00:37:20,040
 kad mu dijete dođe i kaže,

1196
00:37:20,040 --> 00:37:20,920
 tata, mama,

1197
00:37:20,920 --> 00:37:21,420
 ja sam se tako ljeto.

1198
00:37:21,420 --> 00:37:23,360
 Kojeg praktički dijete pošelje na ispovjedno.

1199
00:37:23,360 --> 00:37:24,480
 Tako i onda vidite,

1200
00:37:24,480 --> 00:37:27,860
 samo kako je se jednostavno to prenosilo,

1201
00:37:27,860 --> 00:37:29,580
 taj žar se prenosio

1202
00:37:29,580 --> 00:37:30,760
 i evo,

1203
00:37:30,760 --> 00:37:32,260
 to je nekako bilo,

1204
00:37:32,260 --> 00:37:34,100
 ono što smo prepoznali,

1205
00:37:34,100 --> 00:37:36,260
 da bi mogli dati Zagrebu,

1206
00:37:36,260 --> 00:37:38,300
 Zagrebačkoj biskupiji,

1207
00:37:38,300 --> 00:37:39,700
 koja je jako bogata

1208
00:37:39,700 --> 00:37:41,180
 i sa svećenicima,

1209
00:37:41,400 --> 00:37:42,400
 sa programima,

1210
00:37:42,400 --> 00:37:45,420
 sa pastoralnim načinima rada.

1211
00:37:45,420 --> 00:37:48,480
 I ono što ste vi sami zaključili,

1212
00:37:48,480 --> 00:37:51,600
 da je to polučilo jedan veliki uspjeh,

1213
00:37:51,600 --> 00:37:53,620
 jer su stvarno redovi nekad bili,

1214
00:37:53,620 --> 00:37:55,320
 ono, ne do prve ceste,

1215
00:37:55,320 --> 00:37:58,440
 nego skroz dolje, do kraja.

1216
00:37:58,440 --> 00:38:02,600
 I mi smo stvarno često morali

1217
00:38:02,600 --> 00:38:04,880
 pribjegavati tome,

1218
00:38:04,880 --> 00:38:07,260
 da smo zvali našu braću

1219
00:38:07,260 --> 00:38:08,640
 iz drugih biskupija,

1220
00:38:08,640 --> 00:38:10,960
 da nam dođu pomoći,

1221
00:38:11,040 --> 00:38:11,780
 i tako dalje.

1222
00:38:11,780 --> 00:38:14,380
 Malo ću vas, Don Giuliano,

1223
00:38:14,380 --> 00:38:16,140
 pitati o strukturi zajednice.

1224
00:38:16,140 --> 00:38:17,160
 Dakle, poznato je,

1225
00:38:17,160 --> 00:38:18,480
 unutar crkve,

1226
00:38:18,480 --> 00:38:19,440
 da je vaša zajednica,

1227
00:38:19,440 --> 00:38:21,100
 ono, upravo,

1228
00:38:21,100 --> 00:38:23,300
 po tom brzo rastučem broju

1229
00:38:23,300 --> 00:38:24,040
 svećenika, zvanjača,

1230
00:38:24,040 --> 00:38:25,640
 častnosti stara,

1231
00:38:25,640 --> 00:38:26,260
 i tako dalje.

1232
00:38:27,840 --> 00:38:29,160
 koliko imate svećenika?

1233
00:38:29,160 --> 00:38:30,680
 Mislim, gdje su raspoređeni?

1234
00:38:30,680 --> 00:38:33,200
 Vi ste započeli zapravo u Riječkoj nadbiskupiji,

1235
00:38:33,200 --> 00:38:35,020
 tamo ih je možda i najviše još uvijek,

1236
00:38:35,020 --> 00:38:39,440
 ili kako je zlata slika da dobiju gledatelji sliku zajednice?

1237
00:38:39,440 --> 00:38:43,660
 Zapravo, zajednica je započela još 2005. godine

1238
00:38:43,660 --> 00:38:45,600
 u Zadarskoj nadbiskupiji,

1239
00:38:45,600 --> 00:38:47,260
 kasnije se širila na Riječku

1240
00:38:47,260 --> 00:38:49,780
 i otuda na druge biskupije,

1241
00:38:49,780 --> 00:38:52,680
 dijelom i u Krk,

1242
00:38:52,680 --> 00:38:53,900
 po rečku, Pulsku

1243
00:38:53,900 --> 00:38:56,260
 i sada prema Zagrebu.

1244
00:38:56,260 --> 00:38:58,820
 Sada ima zaređena naša zajednica

1245
00:38:58,820 --> 00:39:01,360
 30 svećenika

1246
00:39:01,360 --> 00:39:05,080
 i negdje 20 podmlatka,

1247
00:39:05,080 --> 00:39:05,740
 znači što,

1248
00:39:05,740 --> 00:39:07,280
 tu su dva džakona,

1249
00:39:07,280 --> 00:39:09,260
 imamo, ja mislim,

1250
00:39:09,260 --> 00:39:12,720
 da, 7 bogoslova

1251
00:39:12,720 --> 00:39:14,720
 i 8 kandidata,

1252
00:39:14,720 --> 00:39:20,980
 znači 20 koji su još u formaciji

1253
00:39:20,980 --> 00:39:22,060
 da budu svećenici,

1254
00:39:22,060 --> 00:39:22,780
 a s druge strane,

1255
00:39:22,780 --> 00:39:24,320
 neovisno o nama,

1256
00:39:24,320 --> 00:39:26,540
 dijeluju sestre koje imaju svoju strukturu

1257
00:39:26,540 --> 00:39:27,660
 poput provincije,

1258
00:39:27,660 --> 00:39:31,680
 odnosno kao što je uobičajeno u crkvi,

1259
00:39:31,680 --> 00:39:34,120
 ali javno vjerničko društvo je

1260
00:39:34,120 --> 00:39:36,240
 kao prijelazna faza prema onome,

1261
00:39:36,240 --> 00:39:39,920
 prema razvoju redovničke zajednice,

1262
00:39:39,920 --> 00:39:41,700
 znači tu su aktivne sestre

1263
00:39:41,700 --> 00:39:43,160
 i kontemplativne sestre,

1264
00:39:43,160 --> 00:39:44,380
 njih oko 50-ak,

1265
00:39:44,380 --> 00:39:46,240
 koji isto, ovaj,

1266
00:39:46,240 --> 00:39:49,480
 dijeluju u različitim biskupijama,

1267
00:39:49,480 --> 00:39:50,720
 u različitim službama,

1268
00:39:50,720 --> 00:39:53,700
 pa evo, ne znam,

1269
00:39:53,700 --> 00:39:55,200
 od toga da su,

1270
00:39:55,200 --> 00:39:56,980
 da rade u karitasima,

1271
00:39:56,980 --> 00:39:57,700
 hospicijima,

1272
00:39:57,700 --> 00:40:00,700
 rade u župnome pastoralu,

1273
00:40:00,700 --> 00:40:02,860
 rade u,

1274
00:40:04,180 --> 00:40:06,200
 gdje se pojavi potreba,

1275
00:40:06,200 --> 00:40:08,040
 znači na usluzi su,

1276
00:40:08,040 --> 00:40:10,720
 evo, skrbe za umirovljene biskupe,

1277
00:40:10,720 --> 00:40:12,220
 za dva umirovljena biskupa,

1278
00:40:12,220 --> 00:40:14,780
 i tako, evo,

1279
00:40:14,780 --> 00:40:18,340
 gdje se pojavi pastoralna potreba,

1280
00:40:18,340 --> 00:40:19,860
 koja je sukladna na našoj karizmi,

1281
00:40:20,420 --> 00:40:21,500
 ovaj sestre,

1282
00:40:21,500 --> 00:40:22,880
 sestre se uključuju.

1283
00:40:23,220 --> 00:40:24,540
 Kad je izrašla ova informacija

1284
00:40:24,540 --> 00:40:26,240
 u petak o uhičenju,

1285
00:40:26,240 --> 00:40:27,640
 onda se nekako steko dojam

1286
00:40:27,640 --> 00:40:28,320
 da ste vi neka,

1287
00:40:28,320 --> 00:40:30,480
 ono, ilegalna zajednica u crkvi,

1288
00:40:30,480 --> 00:40:32,440
 zapravo u nekoj sivoj zoni,

1289
00:40:32,440 --> 00:40:33,040
 i da,

1290
00:40:33,040 --> 00:40:34,480
 neki mračnjaci,

1291
00:40:34,480 --> 00:40:35,920
 za koji se ne zna što radi,

1292
00:40:35,920 --> 00:40:37,380
 zato sam vas zapravo izvao

1293
00:40:37,380 --> 00:40:38,320
 da se, ono, vidi,

1294
00:40:38,320 --> 00:40:40,760
 da se dozna istina ta o društvu,

1295
00:40:40,760 --> 00:40:41,360
 ovlija deo.

1296
00:40:41,360 --> 00:40:44,200
 Koji je vaš službeni neki crkvenist?

1297
00:40:44,200 --> 00:40:45,020
 Evo, kad smo kod častnice,

1298
00:40:45,020 --> 00:40:45,760
 sad samo da završim.

1299
00:40:45,760 --> 00:40:46,900
 Dakle, da je sve ok.

1300
00:40:47,280 --> 00:40:48,820
 Dakle, ja sam čuvao kod redovnica,

1301
00:40:48,820 --> 00:40:49,600
 znali su mi reći,

1302
00:40:49,600 --> 00:40:50,840
 one nisu prave redovnice,

1303
00:40:50,840 --> 00:40:52,660
 one nemaju zapravo redovničke zavijete,

1304
00:40:52,660 --> 00:40:54,880
 ali oni nisu redovnička zajednica.

1305
00:40:54,880 --> 00:40:56,700
 Ali imamo da se taj partijeljstvom misle

1306
00:40:56,700 --> 00:40:57,540
 o iste pravni.

1307
00:40:57,540 --> 00:40:59,340
 Da, o čemu se darko radi,

1308
00:40:59,340 --> 00:41:02,240
 ljudi jednostavno ne razumiju

1309
00:41:02,240 --> 00:41:04,480
 redovnička zajednica,

1310
00:41:04,480 --> 00:41:07,100
 ili bilo koja zajednica posvećenog života

1311
00:41:07,100 --> 00:41:08,480
 ne nastaje preko noći.

1312
00:41:08,480 --> 00:41:10,900
 Ne može neko uzeti sad

1313
00:41:10,900 --> 00:41:13,540
 i reći, ja želim biti redovnica,

1314
00:41:13,540 --> 00:41:15,640
 i sad će odmah crkva reći,

1315
00:41:15,640 --> 00:41:16,480
 evo, ti si redovnica.

1316
00:41:17,280 --> 00:41:21,500
 Nego nastanak zajednica ima svoje faze.

1317
00:41:21,500 --> 00:41:24,980
 Upravo, znači, naša zajednica,

1318
00:41:24,980 --> 00:41:27,280
 jel, ovnija deo koja se sastoji

1319
00:41:27,280 --> 00:41:30,380
 od dva krila, krila braća i sestara,

1320
00:41:30,380 --> 00:41:33,840
 koji su, znači, članovi u biti zajednica,

1321
00:41:33,840 --> 00:41:36,240
 ostalo su lajičke obitelji,

1322
00:41:36,240 --> 00:41:37,720
 koji su više prijatelji,

1323
00:41:37,720 --> 00:41:40,580
 molitveni, molitvena podrška,

1324
00:41:40,580 --> 00:41:41,840
 dok se to, jel, ne strukturira.

1325
00:41:41,840 --> 00:41:44,320
 Upravo zbog toga što se zajednica

1326
00:41:44,320 --> 00:41:45,760
 nalazi u tom nastanku,

1327
00:41:46,500 --> 00:41:48,460
 sve je napravljeno po svim,

1328
00:41:48,460 --> 00:41:51,180
 znači, zakonskim propisima

1329
00:41:51,180 --> 00:41:52,600
 katoličke crkve

1330
00:41:52,600 --> 00:41:54,180
 i u suradnje s biskupima.

1331
00:41:54,180 --> 00:41:56,260
 Nijedan korak nije napravljen bez toga.

1332
00:41:56,260 --> 00:41:58,860
 A što kaže praksa, recimo,

1333
00:41:58,860 --> 00:42:01,220
 crkvena u nastanku tih zajednica,

1334
00:42:01,220 --> 00:42:02,720
 odnosno,

1335
00:42:02,720 --> 00:42:04,720
 redovničkih zajednica,

1336
00:42:06,720 --> 00:42:08,700
 one koje idu prema tome putu

1337
00:42:08,700 --> 00:42:09,720
 da budu ustanove,

1338
00:42:09,720 --> 00:42:11,840
 da budu samostalne na neki način,

1339
00:42:11,840 --> 00:42:14,360
 karizme koje će unutar crkve

1340
00:42:14,360 --> 00:42:15,860
 dobiti svoju strukturu.

1341
00:42:15,860 --> 00:42:19,020
 Ovo što je rekao Don Giuliano,

1342
00:42:19,020 --> 00:42:20,620
 jedne provincije,

1343
00:42:20,620 --> 00:42:22,200
 imamo Isusovce,

1344
00:42:22,200 --> 00:42:23,000
 Salesijance,

1345
00:42:23,000 --> 00:42:27,160
 razne te crkvene zajednice,

1346
00:42:27,160 --> 00:42:28,780
 koje su isto tako nastale

1347
00:42:28,780 --> 00:42:31,060
 u jednom povijesnom trenutku crkve.

1348
00:42:31,660 --> 00:42:32,540
 Što je važno,

1349
00:42:32,540 --> 00:42:36,920
 znači zajednica u tom svom prvom dijelu

1350
00:42:36,920 --> 00:42:41,580
 2003. ženska, 2005. muška,

1351
00:42:41,580 --> 00:42:43,880
 ima taj svoj korijen

1352
00:42:43,880 --> 00:42:45,100
 u molitvenoj zajednice

1353
00:42:45,100 --> 00:42:46,960
 koji su započeli Don Jospi,

1354
00:42:46,960 --> 00:42:49,040
 majka Jozefina, 1998.

1355
00:42:49,040 --> 00:42:50,960
 Ono su to počeli

1356
00:42:50,960 --> 00:42:54,660
 čisto da prodube molitveni života,

1357
00:42:54,660 --> 00:42:58,440
 kao jedna zajednica molitve i slično.

1358
00:42:58,440 --> 00:42:59,680
 Međutim,

1359
00:43:00,180 --> 00:43:02,840
 kada, budući da su i vi sami znate

1360
00:43:02,840 --> 00:43:03,880
 kao lajk,

1361
00:43:03,880 --> 00:43:05,760
 da su ljudi žedni, gladni,

1362
00:43:05,760 --> 00:43:06,440
 traže,

1363
00:43:06,440 --> 00:43:09,360
 tako upravo se dogodilo je

1364
00:43:09,360 --> 00:43:10,400
 s našom zajednicom.

1365
00:43:10,400 --> 00:43:11,940
 Ljudi koji su ih upoznavali,

1366
00:43:11,940 --> 00:43:14,440
 željeli su nalaziti se,

1367
00:43:14,440 --> 00:43:15,360
 dolaziti,

1368
00:43:15,360 --> 00:43:18,620
 hodočastiti i tako dalje.

1369
00:43:18,620 --> 00:43:20,280
 I tu, znači,

1370
00:43:20,280 --> 00:43:22,160
 ono što poštuje

1371
00:43:22,160 --> 00:43:24,380
 naravni taj princip

1372
00:43:24,380 --> 00:43:26,160
 ljudskog udruživanja,

1373
00:43:26,160 --> 00:43:27,300
 poštuje sama crkva

1374
00:43:27,300 --> 00:43:29,380
 i zato je kanonskim zakonnikom

1375
00:43:29,380 --> 00:43:30,760
 dozvolila,

1376
00:43:30,760 --> 00:43:33,020
 znači, to pravo na udruživanje

1377
00:43:33,020 --> 00:43:34,280
 koje imamo krštenjem

1378
00:43:34,280 --> 00:43:36,920
 u našoj katoličkoj crkvi

1379
00:43:36,920 --> 00:43:38,140
 po zakonu,

1380
00:43:38,140 --> 00:43:39,900
 a za svećenike

1381
00:43:39,900 --> 00:43:41,800
 i one koji žele ići

1382
00:43:41,800 --> 00:43:43,460
 putem posvećenog života

1383
00:43:43,460 --> 00:43:44,360
 ili redovničkog,

1384
00:43:44,460 --> 00:43:45,660
 to je i preporučeno

1385
00:43:45,660 --> 00:43:48,100
 da crkva i prepoznaje

1386
00:43:48,100 --> 00:43:49,240
 i razlučuje

1387
00:43:49,240 --> 00:43:50,380
 i podupire.

1388
00:43:50,380 --> 00:43:52,040
 I što je se dogodilo?

1389
00:43:52,040 --> 00:43:53,880
 Kako se oko Don Josipa

1390
00:43:53,880 --> 00:43:56,020
 okupljao sve veći broj

1391
00:43:56,020 --> 00:43:57,680
 mladih koji su, evo,

1392
00:43:57,680 --> 00:43:59,120
 Don Julijano je bio

1393
00:43:59,120 --> 00:44:00,020
 najbolji student

1394
00:44:00,020 --> 00:44:01,120
 u Rijeci medicine,

1395
00:44:01,120 --> 00:44:03,660
 primio nagradu dekana,

1396
00:44:03,660 --> 00:44:05,840
 najbolji student u Splitu,

1397
00:44:05,840 --> 00:44:07,940
 promišljao je o ovom,

1398
00:44:07,940 --> 00:44:09,780
 onom, razne specializacije,

1399
00:44:10,420 --> 00:44:11,460
 ostavio je sve,

1400
00:44:11,460 --> 00:44:13,520
 krenuo s Don Josipom

1401
00:44:13,520 --> 00:44:14,940
 zajedno sa drugom braćom,

1402
00:44:14,940 --> 00:44:16,960
 još jednim liječnikom,

1403
00:44:16,960 --> 00:44:19,500
 jednim zubnim tehničarom,

1404
00:44:19,500 --> 00:44:21,060
 znači to su razna zanimanja

1405
00:44:21,060 --> 00:44:22,460
 koja se nikad ne bi našla.

1406
00:44:22,460 --> 00:44:25,020
 Biskup koji je to prepoznao,

1407
00:44:25,020 --> 00:44:26,200
 dao je dozvolu,

1408
00:44:26,200 --> 00:44:27,460
 pozvo je, evo,

1409
00:44:27,460 --> 00:44:28,820
 možete biti s njim,

1410
00:44:28,820 --> 00:44:30,880
 razmišljate o pozivu,

1411
00:44:30,880 --> 00:44:32,800
 uključit ćete se u bogosloviju

1412
00:44:32,800 --> 00:44:34,740
 i tako iz jedne faze,

1413
00:44:34,740 --> 00:44:35,880
 možemo reći,

1414
00:44:35,880 --> 00:44:37,500
 zajedništva de facto,

1415
00:44:37,500 --> 00:44:39,200
 potpuno legitimnog

1416
00:44:39,200 --> 00:44:41,580
 i preporučenog od crkve.

1417
00:44:41,580 --> 00:44:43,760
 Crkva je u jednom trenutku,

1418
00:44:43,760 --> 00:44:44,920
 kako je to raslo,

1419
00:44:44,920 --> 00:44:47,240
 i među djevojkama

1420
00:44:47,240 --> 00:44:48,200
 koje se odlučile

1421
00:44:48,200 --> 00:44:49,480
 za posvećeni život,

1422
00:44:49,480 --> 00:44:51,400
 i među mladićima,

1423
00:44:51,400 --> 00:44:55,460
 u osobi nadbiskupa Ivana Dejučića

1424
00:44:55,460 --> 00:44:56,820
 odlučila dati tome

1425
00:44:56,820 --> 00:44:58,500
 jednu pravnu strukturu.

1426
00:44:58,500 --> 00:44:59,360
 Zašto?

1427
00:44:59,360 --> 00:45:00,980
 Jer kad imate,

1428
00:45:00,980 --> 00:45:02,540
 već je tad bilo oko

1429
00:45:02,540 --> 00:45:05,100
 dvadesetak sestara,

1430
00:45:05,100 --> 00:45:08,260
 oko 15-16 svećenika,

1431
00:45:08,480 --> 00:45:08,980
 braće,

1432
00:45:08,980 --> 00:45:11,360
 nadbiskup je razmišljao

1433
00:45:11,360 --> 00:45:12,460
 da je šteta,

1434
00:45:12,460 --> 00:45:14,540
 vidi da to privlači mlade,

1435
00:45:14,540 --> 00:45:17,400
 vidi da ima

1436
00:45:17,400 --> 00:45:19,300
 blagoslovljene,

1437
00:45:19,300 --> 00:45:20,900
 blagotvorne,

1438
00:45:20,900 --> 00:45:22,860
 blagotvoran jako utjecaj

1439
00:45:22,860 --> 00:45:23,720
 na pastoral,

1440
00:45:23,720 --> 00:45:24,820
 na služenje,

1441
00:45:24,820 --> 00:45:27,160
 na odgovor na potrebe ljudi

1442
00:45:27,160 --> 00:45:28,660
 u vremenu u kojem živimo.

1443
00:45:29,280 --> 00:45:31,060
 On je savjetovao se

1444
00:45:31,060 --> 00:45:33,400
 sa raznim stručnjacima

1445
00:45:33,400 --> 00:45:34,600
 što se tiče toga

1446
00:45:34,600 --> 00:45:35,940
 i odlučio,

1447
00:45:35,940 --> 00:45:36,620
 znači,

1448
00:45:36,620 --> 00:45:39,700
 osnovati jednim dekretom

1449
00:45:39,700 --> 00:45:41,640
 javno-vjeničko društvo

1450
00:45:41,640 --> 00:45:43,780
 s ciljem da postane

1451
00:45:43,780 --> 00:45:45,940
 ustanova posvećenog života.

1452
00:45:45,940 --> 00:45:47,420
 Što to znači?

1453
00:45:47,420 --> 00:45:48,600
 Javno-vjeničko društvo,

1454
00:45:48,600 --> 00:45:49,580
 kao takvo,

1455
00:45:49,580 --> 00:45:50,880
 ono je,

1456
00:45:50,880 --> 00:45:51,820
 znači,

1457
00:45:51,820 --> 00:45:53,460
 temelj njegov je u tome

1458
00:45:53,460 --> 00:45:55,660
 da je ono utemeljeno

1459
00:45:55,660 --> 00:45:56,920
 na slobodnoj volji

1460
00:45:56,920 --> 00:45:58,920
 onih koji su odlučili udružiti.

1461
00:45:58,920 --> 00:46:00,620
 Ali kad crkva vidi

1462
00:46:00,620 --> 00:46:02,000
 da oni imaju želju,

1463
00:46:02,000 --> 00:46:02,300
 znači,

1464
00:46:02,300 --> 00:46:04,180
 nije to samo karitativni rad,

1465
00:46:04,180 --> 00:46:05,620
 nije to pomaganje

1466
00:46:05,620 --> 00:46:06,840
 samo siromasima,

1467
00:46:06,840 --> 00:46:08,780
 nije to neka samo

1468
00:46:08,780 --> 00:46:10,160
 molitvena grupa

1469
00:46:10,160 --> 00:46:10,840
 koja se moli,

1470
00:46:10,840 --> 00:46:12,600
 nego oni žele evangelizirati,

1471
00:46:12,600 --> 00:46:15,040
 žele voditi kateheze,

1472
00:46:15,040 --> 00:46:17,140
 žele prihvaćati mlade

1473
00:46:17,140 --> 00:46:18,360
 koji bi se formirali

1474
00:46:18,360 --> 00:46:19,120
 u nekom duhu

1475
00:46:19,120 --> 00:46:20,100
 i u nekoj karizmi,

1476
00:46:20,100 --> 00:46:21,600
 crkva, znači,

1477
00:46:21,600 --> 00:46:22,820
 tada preporuča,

1478
00:46:22,940 --> 00:46:23,940
 ako prepoznaje

1479
00:46:23,940 --> 00:46:25,760
 da su to slični ciljevi

1480
00:46:25,760 --> 00:46:27,960
 koji ima crkva po sebi,

1481
00:46:27,960 --> 00:46:29,340
 evangelizacije,

1482
00:46:29,340 --> 00:46:30,300
 formacije,

1483
00:46:30,300 --> 00:46:32,700
 promicanja duhovnih zvanja,

1484
00:46:32,700 --> 00:46:34,260
 crkva tu daje,

1485
00:46:34,260 --> 00:46:35,420
 znači,

1486
00:46:35,420 --> 00:46:36,300
 mogućnost,

1487
00:46:36,300 --> 00:46:37,460
 ukoliko vi,

1488
00:46:37,460 --> 00:46:39,080
 ukoliko zajednica prihvati,

1489
00:46:39,080 --> 00:46:40,300
 da bude osnovana

1490
00:46:40,300 --> 00:46:42,220
 kao javnovjerničko društvo,

1491
00:46:42,220 --> 00:46:42,660
 znači,

1492
00:46:42,660 --> 00:46:43,640
 što to znači,

1493
00:46:43,640 --> 00:46:46,620
 da dijeluje u ime crkve,

1494
00:46:46,620 --> 00:46:48,440
 suodgovorna s crkom

1495
00:46:48,440 --> 00:46:50,220
 i da promiče iste ciljeve.

1496
00:46:50,220 --> 00:46:51,460
 To su, kako smo rekli,

1497
00:46:51,460 --> 00:46:52,660
 evangelizacija,

1498
00:46:52,660 --> 00:46:54,020
 duhovni raz,

1499
00:46:54,020 --> 00:46:54,820
 duhovni život,

1500
00:46:54,820 --> 00:46:56,160
 sakramentalni život

1501
00:46:56,160 --> 00:46:59,040
 i u tome svemu,

1502
00:46:59,040 --> 00:47:00,120
 znači,

1503
00:47:00,120 --> 00:47:02,520
 taj okvir javnog vjerničkog društva

1504
00:47:02,520 --> 00:47:03,760
 s ciljem da postane

1505
00:47:03,760 --> 00:47:04,660
 u budućnosti

1506
00:47:04,660 --> 00:47:07,520
 ustanova posvećenog života

1507
00:47:07,520 --> 00:47:09,900
 prema praksi kongregacije

1508
00:47:09,900 --> 00:47:10,900
 i dokumentima,

1509
00:47:10,900 --> 00:47:12,660
 mora već u toj fazi

1510
00:47:14,080 --> 00:47:17,540
 imati sve elemente

1511
00:47:17,540 --> 00:47:19,880
 kakvim želi postati.

1512
00:47:19,880 --> 00:47:22,040
 Zato, kad smo mi dekretom

1513
00:47:22,040 --> 00:47:23,640
 osnovani,

1514
00:47:23,640 --> 00:47:25,520
 Riječkoga nadbiskupa,

1515
00:47:25,520 --> 00:47:26,960
 ta

1516
00:47:26,960 --> 00:47:32,780
 struktura javnog vjerničkog društva

1517
00:47:32,780 --> 00:47:34,420
 je ad eksperimentum,

1518
00:47:34,420 --> 00:47:35,280
 jer upravo

1519
00:47:35,280 --> 00:47:37,580
 to eksperimentiranje,

1520
00:47:37,580 --> 00:47:38,720
 da vi,

1521
00:47:38,720 --> 00:47:39,680
 znači,

1522
00:47:39,680 --> 00:47:41,660
 strukturirate zajednicu

1523
00:47:41,660 --> 00:47:44,180
 kao buduću redovničku zajednicu,

1524
00:47:44,180 --> 00:47:45,800
 da se tako ponašate,

1525
00:47:45,800 --> 00:47:46,640
 živite,

1526
00:47:46,640 --> 00:47:47,380
 molite,

1527
00:47:47,380 --> 00:47:48,040
 radite.

1528
00:47:48,680 --> 00:47:49,180
 Zašto?

1529
00:47:49,180 --> 00:47:50,640
 Jer crkva ne želi,

1530
00:47:50,640 --> 00:47:52,700
 sad neko izrazi

1531
00:47:52,700 --> 00:47:54,020
 s to ljudi želju

